#

#
# Mapping controls
#
# Description:
#
# Attempts to maintain individual leg/foot animation "feel" by maximum adjustments.
#
# Maintains foot -> leg length relationship.
# Maintains foot -> hip relationship
# Maintains foot -> ground relationship, adjusts root accordingly.
#
# Attempts to maintain individual arm animation "feel" yet maintaining hand to hand relationship.
#	Maintains potential weapon relationship BASED on a weapon scaled in length by 60%.
#  Note: The limb root offset is never used in arms due to no reference pose in .smd files
#

rootScaleJoint ValveBiped.Bip01_L_Foot
rootScaleAmount 1.0
toeFloorZ 2.7777

twoJointIKSolve ValveBiped.Bip01_L_Foot
reverseSolve 0
extremityScale 1.0
limbRootOffsetScale 1.0 1.0 1.0

twoJointIKSolve ValveBiped.Bip01_R_Foot
reverseSolve 0
extremityScale 1.0
limbRootOffsetScale 1.0 1.0 1.0

oneJointPlaneConstraint ValveBiped.Bip01_L_Toe0

oneJointPlaneConstraint ValveBiped.Bip01_R_Toe0

twoJointIKSolve ValveBiped.Bip01_R_Hand
reverseSolve 1
extremityScale 1.0
limbRootOffsetScale 0.0 0.0 0.0

twoJointIKSolve ValveBiped.Bip01_L_Hand
reverseSolve 1
extremityScale 1.0
limbRootOffsetScale 0.0 0.0 0.0
relativeLock ValveBiped.Bip01_R_Hand .6
